pullRequest.title: Backport of latest 1.15.2 mappings back to 1.14.4.
pullRequest.bodyText:
What has be done:

Updated Gradle and build script with the latest ones in the 1.15.2 branch.
Classes with the same intermediary as the 1.15 ones got renamed (unless newer ones are unmapped).
Methods with the same intermediary and signature as the 1.15 ones got renamed (might got mismatch which needs some reviews)
Fields with the same type and intermediary as the 1.15 ones got renamed.
Comments got backported.
Method arguments got backported.
